page.title: 10Children's Views Continued
page.content:
{Jodie Uphill 7 years and months
I like living in Parkstone because I can go to the beach a lot and there are lots of parks to play in and I live near my nanny and I live near a lot of sweet shops and toy shops. ______________________________________ {Travis Board 7 years and 10 months
I would rather be living in Bournemouth because I use to live by my friend Colin. He is my cousin. I am 7 and Colin is 7 as well. I still go to his house sometimes. ______________________________________
